debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment?
debrief.response: The experiment required that I identify the number or letter on the screen and sort it accordingly. Before doing so, a shape appears on the screen indicating the amount of points earned for answering quickly. I was asked to alternate between top and bottom values. If a number was less than 153, I would press j on the keyboard (k for greater). If a letter was closer to a, then I would press d on the keyboard (f if it was closer to z)
